Package com.catchoom.api

Interface Summary
CatchoomResponseHandler CatchoomResponseHanlder expose the interface used by the Catchoom requests to perform callbacks once they have finished.
 

Class Summary
Catchoom Catchoom allows you to send requests to the Catchoom Recognition Server.
Catchoom.Request  
CatchoomErrorResponseItem CatchoomErrorResponseItem is used to comunicate to a CatchoomResponseHandler an error raised during a request.
CatchoomSearchResponseItem CatchoomSearchResponseItem represents the response from the Catchoom Recognition Server for one coincidence within a collection.
